{
  "name": "Defend Other",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/guardian.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When an ally within your threatened area is the target of an attack roll, you may spend an immediate action to grant them a competence bonus to their armor class equal to 1/2 your base attack bonus (rounded down, minimum +1) against that attack. If this attack would still hit, you may choose to take the damage in your ally&#8217;s place.</p>\n<p>If you possess the (patrol) package, when using this talent you may move to put the ally within your reach (with the normal limits for moving as part of your patrol) as part of activating this talent.</p>\n",
